premise_source_doc_sentence: Brother Records , Inc.  (  BRI  )  is a holding company established in 1967 that holds the intellectual property rights of The Beach Boys , including `` The Beach Boys '' trademark .
Prior to being incorporated , Brother Records was a record label founded by Beach Boys ' manager Nick Grillo in October 1966 .
Its output was distributed by Capitol Records in 1967 , and then Reprise Records throughout 1970 -- 78 .
